<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h4> Invitation to interview for the position of <%=  @candidate_interview_schedule.candidate_form.vacancy_request.vacancy %>
    </h4>
     
    <p>
     	Dear <b><%= @candidate_interview_schedule.candidate_form.try(:name) %></b> ,<br><br>

     	Thank you for applying in our company .<br><br> 

     	Your application for the position of <b><%=  @candidate_interview_schedule.candidate_form.vacancy_request.vacancy %></b> stood out to us and we would like to invite you for an interview at our office <b><%= @candidate_interview_schedule.address %></b> to get to know you a bit better.<br>
    </p>
    <p>
     	Your interview is schedule with the <% employee1 = Employee.find_by(id: @candidate_interview_schedule.interviewer_id) %> <b> <%= employee1.try(:first_name) %> <%= employee1.try(:middle_name) %> <%= employee1.try(:last_name) %>.</b> The interview is<b> <%= @candidate_interview_schedule.interview_type_master.try(:name) %></b> and youâ€™ll have the chance to discuss the Job position and learn more about our company .<br> 
    </p>
    <p>
     	Would you be available on <b><%= @candidate_interview_schedule.date %></b> at <b><%= @candidate_interview_schedule.time %>?</b><br>

    </p><br>
    <p>
        Looking forward to hearing from you,<br><br>

        All the best / Kind regards.
     </p>
  </body>
</html>